{
  "2379350": {
    "name": "乱斗骑士大逃杀：Scramble Knights Royale",
    "steam_appid": 2379350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《乱斗骑士大逃杀》！在这款经典冒险风格的大逃杀中，与 32 名骑士一较高下，成为活到最后的骑士，赢得公主的芳心！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/cf4f31b2b73482233518676093ab6e89.poster.avif?t=1771867346\" width=1170 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/cf4f31b2b73482233518676093ab6e89.webm?t=1771867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从船上一跃而下，乘着大乌龟的背游向岸边，开始你的冒险旅程吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/ad549093a61b927fe5c0f71f14935e5e.avif?t=1771867346\" width=1500 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/86da9325674c22c651885f8903e960d3.poster.avif?t=1771867346\" width=1170 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/86da9325674c22c651885f8903e960d3.webm?t=1771867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上这片生机盎然的群岛，攻略地牢、解开谜题并发现宝藏！游戏的每一局都会是独一无二的冒险旅程。快在安全圈缩小、迫使所有骑士正面交锋前完成任务并找到宝藏来做好准备吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/5e9e9f8d2f11f3c509d0e3517d264831.poster.avif?t=1771867346\" width=1170 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/5e9e9f8d2f11f3c509d0e3517d264831.webm?t=1771867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的冒险旅途中一路拾取或购买更强的新装备来强化自己，或在铁匠处花费宝石来升级装备。只要善用策略搭配装备，就能打造强力配装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/1bc75c4c39a64aba9d17653aa7bb0286.poster.avif?t=1771867346\" width=1170 height=546 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/1bc75c4c39a64aba9d17653aa7bb0286.webm?t=1771867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和敌方骑士短兵相接时，你就得靠自己亲手打造的配装，在讲究操作与策略的战斗中取得优势。游戏中的每种武器都有大量不同的招式等着你掌握，地图中也充满了各种适合乱斗的有趣场景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其他特色：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >家园系统：你战场之外的小天地。你能随着冒险进度解锁更多物品来装饰这里，还能和朋友一起在这里放松休息。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >秀出你的帅气骑士：只要游玩不同的赛季即可解锁大量自定义外观与饰品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一起游玩：你能和朋友组队一起匹配进入混战模式，也能组队游玩我们即将在今年晚些时候推出的双排模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在线分屏：在沙发上体验本地分屏多人游玩，或者一起对战在线玩家！快找个朋友一起开黑吧！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >倒下还能“咕”：你出局后，可以变成一只小鸡来观战。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                              <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/37efd838bca4635d75df502dcaeb5d17.poster.avif?t=1771867346\" width=144 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379350/extras/37efd838bca4635d75df502dcaeb5d17.webm?t=1771867346\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
